sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Service as Model Registry Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Registry as model-registry REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP Optional TLS

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 1: External User Access (Secured)

    Client->>Router: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/models<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Router->>Service: Forward (TLS reencrypt)
    Service->>Proxy: HTTPS Request
    Proxy->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>Validate Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Proxy: Authorization Result
    Proxy->>Registry: Forward to localhost:8080<br/>HTTP (no encryption)
    Registry->>DB: Query/Insert Metadata<br/>PostgreSQL Protocol<br/>Auth: Password/Cert
    DB-->>Registry: Result
    Registry-->>Proxy: JSON Response
    Proxy-->>Service: HTTPS Response
    Service-->>Router: HTTPS Response
    Router-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 2: Internal Access (No Proxy)

    participant InternalPod as Internal Pod
    InternalPod->>Service: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/models<br/>Port 8080 HTTP
    Service->>Registry: HTTP Request (no auth)
    Registry->>DB: Query Metadata
    DB-->>Registry: Result
    Registry-->>Service: JSON Response
    Service-->>InternalPod: JSON Response

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 3: Operator Reconciliation

    participant Operator as controller-manager
    participant Webhook as Webhook Service<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS

    Client->>K8sAPI: Create ModelRegistry CR
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate CR<br/>mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validated CR
    K8sAPI->>Operator: CR Event (watch)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Service<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Route<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>ServiceAccount Token
